LINCOLN LAND COMPANY, a Corporation, v. Ralph H. LANPHIER et al. No. 5394. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. July 16, 1956. Robert G. Simmons, Jr., Floyd E. Wright, and Robert M. Harris, Scotts-bluff, Neb., and Mr. Stanley K. Hathaway, Torrington, Wyo., for appellant. R. R. Bostwick, Casper, Wyo., George P. Sawyer, and Hal E. Morris, Torring-ton, Wyo., for appellees.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and PICKETT, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed pursuant to stipulation of counsel.
